org.fpe4j

Class FFXConformanceTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.fpe4j.FFXConformanceTest

  • public class FFXConformanceTest
extends java.lang.Object
    JUnit test cases for conformance with NIST SP 800-38G and the NIST sample data provided at http://csrc.nist.gov/groups/ST/toolkit/examples.html.

    To enable FF1 and FF3 to output the intermediate results shown in the sample data, change Constants.CONFORMANCE_OUTPUT to true.

    Author:
    Kai Johnson
